snippet.title: Celebrities Who SPOKE UP About Amber Heard's Lies | OG CELEBRITY
snippet.description:
Celebrities Who SPOKE UP About Amber Heard's Lies

Johnny Depp and his ex-wife Amber Heard have been involved in different legal battles for years now, and it finally looks like this drama might soon come to an end.
Johnny’s fans are now saying they can’t wait for justice to be finally served and for the court to prove what the fans claim they knew all along–that Amber heard was lying.
And it’s not just Johnny’s fans who always believed the actor was telling the truth, but also his celebrity friends and colleagues.
